### List all books
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/books

### Get a book by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/1

### Create a new book
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Hobbit 2",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "9780547928228",
  "category": "Fantasy",
  "status": "available"
}

### Update a book
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "9780547928227",
  "category": "Fantasy",
  "status": "checked out"
}

### Delete a book
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/1

### Search books by title
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/find?title=Hobbit

### Search books by author
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/find?author=Tolkien

### Search books by category
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/find?category=Fantasy

### Search books by multiple parameters
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/books/find?author=Tolkien&category=Fantasy
